Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:50.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在那崩壞的黑暗中 你哭泣的身影如此清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:59.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}冰冷的門  至今依舊緊閉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:03.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}再也回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:09.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那些過往 那些夢境 那些希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:13.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}這才是天空的本色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:20.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}隨心所欲 肆意變天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:29.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}翻越吧  越向障壁的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:39.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}穿過吧  穿越世界的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:45.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}如四散的塵埃般 消失無蹤  白日夢

Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:50.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}壊れた暗闇　泣いてる君の影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:59.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}冷たい扉が　今でも閉ざされ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:03.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう戻れはしないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:09.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}あの日々　あの夢　あの希望は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:13.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この空は本物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:20.25,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}気まぐれ　突然　色を変えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:29.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}越えて　その壁の向こう側へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:39.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}潜って　行く世界の欠片が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:45.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}はがれ落ちて消えて行くわ　Daydream

Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個垃圾說是想做畫畫相關的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimHei\fad(1900,0)\pos(650,340)\c&H202323&\3c&H9CADAB&\bord5\be2\blur2\fs60\b1}夢{\fs40}不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷奧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼 快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你覺得祭品不合適的話 就換別人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再犧牲一個人準備就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你覺得橘勇魚是特別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就已經把感情拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對鎮上傢伙們的復仇時刻馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些我都明白的 雷奧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才會成為你的「容器」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(準備中)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連身邊最親近的人 被夢魔盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然都沒有發現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有她 我不想讓她捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這與現實和幻界無關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望她能畫自己喜歡的畫就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我把你吵醒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在畫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣 是沒有什麼夢想的畫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明考試就近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 夢路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜裡有點兒吵對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起床看看情況 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候男人需要這樣的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為爸爸這麼說 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲玩得有點兒不順手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 害我白操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也多少準備準備考試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有資格說別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太謝謝你了 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 長翅膀的鯨魚姑娘和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇魚 奶茶好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢路也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你在畫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種生物真的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連沒見過的東西都能畫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在用心眼看著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也想讓在這裡的眼睛看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才畫出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能在這個世界相見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然就說了一句「誒」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是這麼有感覺的台詞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最愛的爸爸和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然夫婦兩人都遇難了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還有那麼小的孩子在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界還真是殘酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還有不少債務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒流浪街頭就已經很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管心裡有多麼結實的城堡 它都會輕易地垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的心情 語言還有事物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中重視的東西越多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的東西也會變得越來越多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母 老師 同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是「僅僅在那裡」一樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既沒有希望也沒有失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不用說夢想還有希望什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對如同空殼一樣的我 只是些礙事的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的你會進入我的牢獄之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許也只是偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對為了向米斯特路汀復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在「現界」中尋找容器的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有感情的你是最合適不過的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢魔 雷斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這無間的牢獄中 成為我的容器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容器…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好名字呢 容器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空空的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫河浪千鶴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動物?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草泥馬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個來店裡吃東西的顧客給了我兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一個我在用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個我想送給河浪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 小魚大人被夢魔給…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 請將你的力量借給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管會發生什麼事 我都想要救勇魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 橘的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止 還沒有什麼變化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格 行動 都還是原來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是會奪取人心的壞夢魔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就因為這樣才危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼時候就會成為海格力斯的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者被米斯特路汀襲擊也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒讓食夢者和你一起來也是這個原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 只有打開協會的門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那個夢魔拽出來 驗明真身才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還不知道是敵人還是夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上 在去學校之前把勇魚帶來可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在既然不知道對方的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越早接觸越好不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 今天醫院和社團都沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很閒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不想打擾她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就明天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 硬來麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要怎麼辦 關於小魚大人的夢魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被瑪莉送回老家的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行得通嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被綁作人質的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小魚大人的夢想也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由衣 如果你重要的人的夢想就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定 會和他是一樣的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…漫長的雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊 找勇魚的話在房間裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用叫她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原夢路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 原來是找夢路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看見他 好像是出門到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡等他可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常歡迎 黑咖啡是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 霧島
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 勇魚和藤原還真是薄情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說過要一起來考試複習的 卻拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當天邀請他們 人家或許也有很多事要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是有要做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「睡午覺 抱著電視直到天亮」by秋柳貴照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不算有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你剛才寫的那個川柳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了逗我笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說是認真寫的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑你了真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是認真寫的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是為了逗你笑才寫的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以霧島你能笑出來 我很高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小就身體不好 不停地輾轉在醫院間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的環境中長大 漸漸的變得不再笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某一天 我或許是受了電視的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開著玩笑讀起了川柳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那是一個十分幼稚的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但妹妹的臉就像太陽一樣綻放出了笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我 也能給別人帶來歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會盡我所能 為更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來歡樂的火種
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是有點兒傷感的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她很快就會好起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個火種一定也將我心中的火點燃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一句 我妹妹她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都能在漢堡店裡打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經痊癒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可喜可賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉了這麼多圈兒了都沒遇見主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經掌握到了這麼絕棒的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快速告訴給主人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再晚點兒說不定就會忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來把那邊兒的也被捲進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個「容器」還有意識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來跟那些傢伙一樣也是好夥伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是酸透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到幻界 我的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊白日做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊做著重複的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真是慾壑難填的生物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是這樣想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是你的熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要做夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只能掠奪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從人類的世界掠奪到幻界來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海格力斯主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘭保夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一條情報想要上報給您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說三葉的同夥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和安琪·三葉在一起的叫做「食夢者」的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們居然想要反抗主人您呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們積極對抗敵人真是勇敢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她們都是膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們一聽說我們用人類的夢想作人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就對我下不了手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您快去打倒她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加同伴的數量才是要緊事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時先不管她們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們成不了什麼氣候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過不了多久 她們就會成為授戒的貢品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,授戒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說那位米斯特路汀也會來這邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 給我來杯熱點的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之前 你有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河浪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天跟你在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽你說「我們一起回去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放鬆了警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到你還留在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 河浪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想跟我說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 難道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河浪 連你也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇魚她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狡猾的樹海困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 不去打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河浪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河浪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是夥伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幅佳作啊 只用一天就完成了真不敢想像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不知道為什麼特別順手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是有點累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉 我們一起洗個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可不要偷窺哦 夢路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我說的跟變態一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是樹海還是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓他對勇魚出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇魚她 被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼時候會到來的樹海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.08,0:23:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼時候會打開的Daydream（白日夢）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在不經意間 門被打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到面前的樹海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到面前的夢魔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字叫 米斯特路汀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 食夢者瑪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止 不會讓你再對勇魚出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.20,0:24:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSimHei\fad(600,0)\pos(424,320)\bord1\blur3\3c&H656565&\b1}夢的守護者

Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:30.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天萬里無雲 洋溢著笑容出行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:45.42,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無顧忌的大吃著 香甜的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:51.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復了精神 就悄悄的想起了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:55.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起裹在棉被中數著羊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:59.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起在輾轉難眠的夜晚 期盼天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:03.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起幻想著明天必到的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:20.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都化為堅強的心 將我籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:30.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容傳遞著希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:35.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定會到來

Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:30.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日は青空　笑顔でお出かけ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:45.42,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘いお菓子　たくさん食べて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:51.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元気になると　そっと　みんなの事思う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.35,0:22:55.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布団を被り　羊数え
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:59.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝を待って　寝れない夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:03.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと明日　楽しくなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:20.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気持ちが強さに変わって　あたしを包む
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:30.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑顔が希望を伝えてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:35.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日がきっと来る

